<h2>Login</h2>

<p>To use Have I Played Bowie Today? you must grant access to your Spotify account.</p>
<p>The following permissions will be requested:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Access to your email address and profile</li>
    <li>Access to your recently played tracks</li>
</ul>

